import Random

## Model

```julia:ex2
@model function m_pois(admit, reject)
   α₁ ~ Normal(0,100)
   α₂ ~ Normal(0,100)

   for i ∈ 1:length(admit)
       λₐ = exp(α₁)
       λᵣ = exp(α₂)
       admit[i] ~ Poisson(λₐ)
       reject[i] ~ Poisson(λᵣ)
   end
end;
```
